{ This move 'threatens to threaten' the bishop on g5. If this bishop retreats Black has got a nice discovered attack on the queen with Nd5 or Ng4. }
11. Rhe1 a6
{ This is a very strong move that has multiple ideas behind it. The most obvious one is that Bb5 is not possible any more - a move that would be annoying after ...Qd7. The main point however is that Black now has a stunning idea that is tough to prevent. }
