4. Qxf4 Bd6 5. Qe3 Nf6 { Black has a huge attack already, for instance } 6. d4
O-O 7. e5 Bb4+ 8. c3 d6 9. cxb4 dxe5 10. dxe5 Re8
{ White has only played with pawns and the queen - don't do that ! } *

