{ I was quite surprised to find more than 1800 games with this move in Mega Database 2018. It is a passive way to play and gives Black an easy game in more than one way. Our general approach is to play ...d5 whenever possible, and there is no reason to do differently here. }
4... d5 5. Bg5
{ That keeps the tension, but gives us the opportunity to gain useful space. }
5... d4 6. Nd5 Be6
{ This is the most forceful, the doubled pawns don't bother Black at all. } 7.
