ack side after 4. d4 as well, so the position types are familiar. }
4. h3
{ The twin move to  4.a3!  White is playing a waiting move, trying to improve his position slightly, but also to just irritate Black a bit. Just as after any slow move, I see no reason not to play  4...d5  . }
