{ Not the most impressive move, but it has been played more than 100 times in Mega2018. Unsurprisingly, Black is fine with about any natural move, but lame play invites the most active response. }
5... Nd4 6. Nxe5
{ The only possible drawback of 5... Nd4, but it is harmless and rather comfortable for Black after the correct reply. }
6... Qe7
{ Simple and effective: Black gets the pawn back quickly and enjoys a good game. }
7. Nf3 Nxb5 8. Nxb5 Qxe4+ 9. Kf1 Qc4+ 10. Qe2+ Qxe2+ 11. Kxe2 Nd5
{ This is the only important idea to remember. Black covers c7 and is ready to answer c4 with a counterattack on b5. }
12. c4 a6 { And Black is already for choice. } *

