{ Here 9... Nf6 is very natural and will most likely transpose to this chapter's mainline after  9...Nf6  10.O-O-O  .   I still suggest playing  9...d5!  ,  immediately threatening ...Nc5 to attack the d3-bishop. If you forget this small detail, it's not the end of the World... but exploiting minor inaccuracies will pay off over time. }
